<example>
  <title>Counter-controlled Loop: Rose printing</title>
  <program>
num = int(input("Enter the desired number of roses: "))

while num > 0:
    print("A rose for you!")
    num = num - 1
print("You could have more!")
  </program>
  <description>Print a number of roses using a while loop according to input</description>
